@Node Main "FTPMount"

                @{b}Welcome to FTPMount!@{ub}
                ====================



  @{b}FTPMount@{ub} allows FTP sites to be mounted as part of an AmigaDOS file
  system.

            @{" Introduction " Link "intro"}    @{" Installation " Link "install"}

            @{" Usage        " Link "usage"}    @{" Options      " Link "options"}

            @{" Restrictions " Link "restrictions"}    @{" Known bugs   " Link "bugs"}

            @{" ToDo List    " Link "todo"}    @{" Changes      " Link "changes"}

